# Vendored verbatim from
# https://github.com/eyereasoner/eye/blob/master/reasoning/entail/socrates.n3
# No truncation needed (7 lines upstream). This is a distinct EYE corpus
# directory from the already-vendored `socrates` case (reasoning/socrates/):
# same rdfs:subClassOf forward-chaining mechanism, but this file is EYE's
# `entail/` example specifically demonstrating single-step "logic entailment"
# (subclass -> membership) rather than the multi-level dog/nixon-diamond
# style hierarchies already covered -- kept because it exercises the same
# distinct minimal entailment shape the upstream `entail` directory targets,
# with its own EYE-checked claim file (`entail/socrates-claim.n3`) confirming
# the answer below.
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.
@prefix : <http://example.org/socrates#>.

:Socrates a :Man.
:Man rdfs:subClassOf :Mortal.

{?A rdfs:subClassOf ?B. ?S a ?A} => {?S a ?B}.
